    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can u go deeper into the moral side of it? like, instead of just saying it helps mobility, can u frame it in a way that shows why the current meritocracy argument is actually kind of a lie or just fundamentally unfair when you consider historical context? i want to make sure my paper makes the opposing view look weak.",
